725490f-a.text:
58th Street (formerly Betts Ave. and also Covert Street, foreground not seen.) at Fifty-sixth Ave. (Note that the 27i story wing was in line of the last mentioned Ave. The house was not standing in 1929.) The owners of this house were Charles G. Covert frocm 1860-1873, and Cord Meyer in 1891. It was formerly designated as 246 Betts Ave.
1922.
View 2: March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
